summary: Just a small house outside Whiterun,  with all crafting stations. This is a nice house for beginners or when you start a new game.
descriptionHtml:
Just a small house outside Whiterun, with all crafting stations and containers. This is a nice house for beginners or when you start a new game.

I'm thinking about moving the entrance somewhere else. This is a very early release of the mod and more features will be added later.

Version 0.5.0 changelog:
- added a unique bow and sword
- added a mine(wip)
- added some misc items
- rearranged some stuff
Version 0.1.1 changelog:
- fixed the entrance bug
- added some random items
- added a chest,bookcase,strongbox

Installation:
Just put the .esp file in the Data folder and activate it in the launcher or NMM.

Uninstallation:
Just disable the mod in the launcher or NMM and remove the .esp file.


Please report any bugs or glitches.
author: Papucho
